snippet.textDisplay:
Okay... first of all, let me put on my protective gear for this one.


It's a good song over a great melody. I don't think that lyrically it really works too much to be honest. Don't get me wrong, he kills it with his performance (his multiple-attempt, cut, chopped, tweaked, tuned and layered performance from the studio, so let's not suck his dick too hard) and you can really hear the emotion in his voice, however I feel this would have been better had they written a new song to fit the atmosphere a little more. Of course, this is just my opinion. I do think this is a great track overall but it's not a masterpiece and does not break the mould. Have a great day!
snippet.textOriginal:
